snippet.title: Bannermen Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A new teaser trailer for the upcoming RTS game Bannermen, developed by the Swedish studio Pathos Interactive.

Be sure to follow our work at Facebook:
https://facebook.com/BannermenGame

Free sign-up for the Bannermen beta:
https://bannermen.net/
